Class Cluster

java.lang.Object
  ants.search.Cluster

public class Cluster
extends java.lang.Object

a cluster is an area on the map. the cluster connects the neighbour cluster throw passable edges along the cluster side. these edges are connected to edge other is there is a passable path between.
